posts.extended: London music documentary (Rap & Grime).The new found fans of the scene have created an economy for many young artists to thrive and have careers as full-time musicians. Here are their stories.Starring: Posty, Elf Kid, Semtex, Morgan Keyz, 67, Nyge, J Hus, Vicky Grout, Belly Squad, SNE, Jevon, Reeko
